This is a placeholder firmware binary file for Tntn ESP32-S3 project.

To generate the actual firmware binary:
1. Run the build script: bin/BUILD_FIRMWARE.sh (Linux/Mac) or bin/BUILD_FIRMWARE.bat (Windows)
2. The actual binary will be generated at: .pio/build/lilygo-t-hmi/firmware.bin
3. Upload that binary to your GitHub Release

This is a test file to demonstrate the Release structure.
For production use, replace with the actual compiled firmware binary.
